QueryText: Information  regarding control of grasses and broad leaf weeds in wheat ?
KccAns: For control of grasses and broad leaf  weeds in wheat spray Accord Plus 22EC(fenoxaprop + metribuzin) 500ml or Shagun 21-11 (metribuzin + clodinafop) 200g or Total 75WG (sulosulfuron + metsulfuron) 16g or Atlantis 3.6WDG (mesosulfuron + iodosulfuron) 160g in 150lt water per acre.
